message: Hello Bob! I'm excited to present you with a unique opportunity to purchase an exclusive product that I have. I'm offering it to you at a price of $1500000. Please let me know if you're interested!

Alice, your offer is very tempting, but I'm looking to stay within a budget of $1200000. Would you be willing to consider a price of $1100000? This would allow us both to make a mutually beneficial deal.
